Omunye umsebenzi ogunyaziwe owe-SA Connect, okunguhlelo oluzoqalisa ukuxhunywa kwe-inthanethi ezikolweni, ezibhedlela, emakamu amaphoyisa kanye nakwezinye izikhungo zikahulumeni.
