Izinhlelo ezinkulu ezine seziphothuliwe futhi zasayinwa kuze kube yinamuhla – eziyingxenye yokuhlangana kwenhlalo - phakathi kwabasebenzi, amabhizinisi, uhulumeni kanye nemiphakathi – sezivele zinomthelela kulezi zimboni.
Ngokuqaliswa kokusebenza koHlelo Lwemboni Yezinkukhu, imboni isitshale imali eyizigidi ezingama-800 zamarandi ukuthuthukisa umkhiqizo.
