UMbutho Wezokuvikela WaseNingizimu Afrika (i-SANDF) kanye noMbutho Wamaphoyisa AseNingizimu Afrika (i-SAPS) iyaqhubeka nokubamba iqhaza ngobuhlakani ezinhlelweni zokuvimbela udweshu kanye nokugcina uxolo kuleli zwekazi.
INingizimu Afrika iyaqhubeka futhi nokusekela imizamo yokuxazulula udweshu kwelaseLesotho, e-Sri Lanka kanye nase-South Sudan, eholwa yiPhini likaMongameli.
Ubambiswano lwezomnotho oluphakathi kwezwe lethu namazwe e-BRICS (i-Brazil, i-India, i-Russia, i-China neNingizimu Afrika) luqinisiwe ngenkathi kusayindwa izivumelwano zokuqala ezimbili eziphakathi kohulumeni balawa mazwe, ngenkathi kubanjwe iNgqungquthela ye-BRICS yesithupha.
