4.2 Ukusungulwa kwama-SEZ ezweni lonke kunciphisa ukugxila kakhulu kwemisebenzi yezomnotho ezindaweni ezithile ezweni ngenxa yokuhlelwa komhlaba kwesikhathi sobandlululo.
4.3 Kusukela ekusungulweni kwawo, ama-SEZ asebe negalelo ekuheheni utshalomalingqo lwamazwe angaphandle, njengotshalomali oluyizigidigidi ezintathu zamarandi olusanda kusayinwa ku-SBIDZ.
