Siyawakhumbula amagama ashiwo ngu-Sol Plaatje, ephawula ngalesi sigameko esibuhlungu kangaka, uma ethi:
“Ngenkathi evuka ekuseni ngoLwesihlanu, mhla zingama-20 kuNhlaba ngowe-1913, umuntu omnyama wazithola, empeleni engesona isigqila, kepha eyisilahlwa, esingafuneki neze ezweni lakhe, azalelwa kulona, futhi lapho inkaba yakhe ikhona.”
Abantu bakithi bahlukumezeka kakhulu futhi bahlangabezana nobunzima obesabekayo ngenxa yokushaywa koMthetho Womhlaba Wabomdabu. Kuze kube namuhla, sisahleli nemithelela kanye nemiphumela emibi yalowo mthetho.
Sibuthene lapha ngesikhathi esinzima kakhulu futhi esinezinselelo eziningi embusweni wethu wentando yeningi labantu osemusha.
Kepha-ke, nakuba kunjalo, sisesikhathini emlandweni wethu lapho kuvunguza khona umoya wethemba elikhulu, lokuthi konke sekuzolunga noma kanjani.
Eminyakeni engama-25 izwe libuswa ngentando yeningi labantu, sesenze inqubekelaphambili enkulu impela ekwakheni isizwe esisha lapho bonke abantu baseNingizimu Afrika benamalungelo alinganayo kanye namathuba angudeda ngendlale.
Eminyakeni engama-25, kuningi esesikwenzile ukuhlangabezana nezidingo zabantu eziyisisekelo, ukunciphisa ububha kanye nokuvuselela kabusha umnotho owabe usufadalele, owabe wenzelwe ukubhekana nezidingo zabayingcosana kuphela.
Ngokusebenzisana kanye nokubambisana, sikwazile ukubeka isisekelo esiqinile esingakhela phezu kwaso izwe lapho bonke abantu bezohlala ngokuthula, banethezeke, futhi bathokoze.
Kepha-ke nakuba kunjalo, sibuthene ngesikhathi lapho izwe lethu libhekene nezinselelo ezinkulu.
Umnotho wethu awukhuli. Futhi aligculisi neze izinga lokwakhiwa kwamathuba omsebenzi.
Lokhu kuyinto esikhathaza ngaphezu kwakho konke okunye.
Kuyinto ethinta wonke umuntu.
Kuthinta wena, nsizwa yaseMzimhlophe, eSoweto, njengoba sekuphele iminyaka emihlanu uqedile esikoleni, kodwa namanje awukawutholi umsebenzi, usahleli ekhaya.
Kubuhlungu futhi nakuwena, msebenzi wase-Nelson Mandela Bay, ngoba phela nakuba ukhona umholo owutholayo, kunzima kakhulu ukwanelisa izidingo zakho zempilo.
